# Git Attributes Configuration
# This file controls how Git handles files in this repository

# Exclude README.md from GitLab exports (but keep it for GitHub)
# When exporting/pushing to GitLab, README.md will be excluded
# When pushing to GitHub, README.md will be included normally
README.md export-ignore

